        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## EUDR-022 Protected Area Validator Alert Rules\n\n| Alert | Condition | Severity | Evaluation |\n|-------|-----------|----------|------------|\n| **Critical Buffer Violations Rate** | Critical buffer violations > 3/hour | Critical | Every 1m, for 5m |\n| **p99 Latency Threshold** | p99 processing latency > 5s | Warning | Every 1m, for 5m |\n| **Error Rate Threshold** | Error rate > 1% | Warning | Every 1m, for 5m |\n| **Unresolved Violations** | Unresolved violations > 15 | Warning | Every 5m, for 10m |\n| **Compliance Score Drop** | Avg compliance score < 60 | Critical | Every 5m, for 15m |\n\n### Notification Channels\n- **Critical**: PagerDuty + Slack #eudr-critical\n- **Warning**: Slack #eudr-alerts + Email on-call\n\n### Runbook Links\n- [Protected Area Violation Response](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/pav/violation-response)\n- [Buffer Zone Encroachment](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/pav/buffer-encroachment)\n- [PADDD Event Response](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/pav/paddd-response)\n- [Performance Degradation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/pav/perf-degradation)\n- [Compliance Score Recovery](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/pav/compliance-recovery)"
      }
